SUMMARY:Are Your Ducks in a Row?
DESCRIPTION:Workshop about Advance Care Planning\nNone of us want to think about it\, right? But at some point in the future\, we all may face a situation where important decisions must be made about our healthcare\, but we are unable to speak for ourselves. Or perhaps this has happened to a loved one. Are you prepared? \nCome to this workshop at the Wilson County Library to learn how to get your ducks in a row. This will be an informative workshop about advanced care planning\, healthcare\, proxies\, legal paperwork\, and will include an interactive exercise that will help to clarify your thoughts.
URL:https://www.transitionslifecare.org/event/are-your-ducks-in-a-row/
LOCATION:Wilson County Library\, 249 Nash St. N\, Wilson\, 27893\, United States
CATEGORIES:Community Events
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://www.transitionslifecare.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/Duck-line-close-no-background-1.png
